CheckFieldConstraint(TextField, FieldValidation.FieldConstraint...) - Static method in class controller.FieldValidation
Validates the text field against any of the FieldConstraint constants passed to the method except the X_GREATER_THAN_EQUAL_Y or X_LESS_THAN_EQUAL_Y constraint checks.
CheckFieldConstraint(TextField, TextField, FieldValidation.FieldConstraint) - Static method in class controller.FieldValidation
Validates whether the integer value of the first text field (X) is greater than or equal to/less than or equal to the integer value of the second text field (Y).
closeChildScreen() - Static method in class controller.MainScreen
Closes the child screen and sets the public static class variable referencing the screen's stage to null.
controller - package controller
The controller package contains classes that support passing user supplied data into the model and updating the user view based on model updates and application logic/rules.
